<div class="lang-sc">
    <section id="what-is">
      <h2>什么是春节？</h2>

      <div class="image-panel">
        <img src="/img/photos/temple-red-lanterns.webp" alt="春节期间挂满红灯笼的传统中国寺庙" loading="lazy">
